        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You were a prostitute; many of your sisters saw it has a punishing existence. You saw it as a true refection of life. The pain, the blood, the truth of things was shown in crystal clarity. Until one day the Madam started beating one of the girls under the suspension of keeping money. Before her hand struck down twice, you had shoved a blade in her eye. The girls looked to you for guidance, you had a better idea. You used the money that was left to get the women new lives in other cities. They never forgot your help and gave you all the information they could. One of the informants told you of a woman who never seemed to age, that she had some magic about her. It was in the town of Zamosc. As you walked to door it opened for you, Putio stood there. You learned at her side, she taught you the secrets of the fruit, how to write the words of magic, how to drink the blood of life. After many years she embraced you. You left with her blessings, and have protected women when they could not protect themselves. You have spent years in and out of torpor, a few months ago you awoke in a scream. One of your childer had died. Across the sea, it has taken you months but you have made it to los angeles, and are trying to find out what has happened to her."
        ],
